South African House Prices Rise 4.2% in August From Year Ago, Absa Says

-- B y   A n t o n y   S g u a z z i n
-- 
2011-09-08T06:25:15Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-08/south-african-house-prices-rise-4-2-in-august-from-year-ago-absa-says.html
House prices in  South Africa  rose
4.2 percent in August from a year ago, accelerating from a 3%
rate the month earlier,  Absa Group Ltd. (ASA)  said in an e-mailed
statement today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Antony Sguazzin at 
 asguazzin@bloomberg.net  